{
  "3158070": {
    "name": "死线勇者",
    "steam_appid": 3158070,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158070/extras/e6f5933f550468087a73ac8b6f116826.avif?t=1762240192\" width=462 height=174 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「死线勇者」是一款结合「番茄钟定时器」、「生产力工作列表」与「放置RPG」要素的游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当你正在专注于工作时，你的英雄会在奇幻世界中探险，击败敌人，并逐渐成长茁壮。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >⌛专注工作=探索世界⌛</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >写下你要做的待办事项，然后立即「开始专注」吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158070/extras/44af1a544c9034861d8903baedc7bc34.poster.avif?t=1762240192\" width=532 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158070/extras/44af1a544c9034861d8903baedc7bc34.webm?t=1762240192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158070/extras/44af1a544c9034861d8903baedc7bc34.mp4?t=1762240192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每当玩家进行「专注」时，你的英雄会持续在游戏中探索，收集游戏资源。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >（这款游戏不会在你专注时有任何的操作需求，请放心去做你手边的事情吧！）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158070/extras/fae1488e416e38cc0935faa8c78a3db6.poster.avif?t=1762240192\" width=532 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158070/extras/fae1488e416e38cc0935faa8c78a3db6.webm?t=1762240192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158070/extras/fae1488e416e38cc0935faa8c78a3db6.mp4?t=1762240192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当专注结束，进入休息阶段时，会随机触发事件或战斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158070/extras/5410546f663adcf803e710e21e6618eb.poster.avif?t=1762240192\" width=532 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158070/extras/5410546f663adcf803e710e21e6618eb.webm?t=1762240192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158070/extras/5410546f663adcf803e710e21e6618eb.mp4?t=1762240192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >认真工作，然后确认你的收获！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >P.S.即使不使用工作列表的功能，也是可以当成一款休闲放置游戏来体验的喔！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🧙‍♂️打造属于你的英雄🧙‍♂️</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >正式版本将支持支持：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超过10种以上的英雄职业！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超过20种以上的生态地图和地牢！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超过100种以上的技能可供组合！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超过2000种道具和武器装备！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中玩家可以选择使用不同职业的英雄，每个职业都有各自的技能与擅长的战斗风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158070/extras/86a195935547e0a472b3090c1c18015d.avif?t=1762240192\" width=532 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >根据对手调整对战策略，才能在战斗中无往不利！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158070/extras/d69d1e5c8af8c33cf974b617ffb7d874.poster.avif?t=1762240192\" width=532 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158070/extras/d69d1e5c8af8c33cf974b617ffb7d874.webm?t=1762240192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158070/extras/d69d1e5c8af8c33cf974b617ffb7d874.mp4?t=1762240192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >📑工作总结📈</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在冒险之余，游戏也会纪录个别任务的花费时间，以及每天的专注时间长度。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可以很方便地回顾自己的工作情况，抓出导致工作真正拖延的「敌人」！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158070/extras/f6b59056b6eebc6d014e2ccf8200438d.avif?t=1762240192\" width=532 height=300 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158070/extras/e89b2091aaf6e2f9e49a0e12bbf53dd3.avif?t=1762240192\" width=532 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
